{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"079314b3f6","title":"晋绥分局应将工业生产放在领导工作的重要位置","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"73a56698dc","index":0,"year":1948,"month":5,"day":11,"articleId":"079314b3f6","article":{}}],"tags":[{"name":"文章","id":"c9f57d6426","type":"文稿类型"},{"name":"毛泽东","id":"dd2b275f6c","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"wenji5","name":"毛泽东文集第五卷（1999）","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"中央文献研究室","files":"/books/wenji5.pdf","articles":[],"comments":[],"contents":[],"pages":[]}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"wenji5":{"comments":[{"id":"bfe644adab","publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{},"index":-1,"part_index":-1,"offset":-1,"text":"根据毛泽东手稿刊印。"}],"contents":[{"id":"40514ac2de","type":"title","text":"晋绥分局应将工业生产放在领导工作的重要位置","index":0,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"2ef3141fd6","type":"paragraph","text":"晋绥分局，并告华北局，西北局：","index":1,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"179eed1f79","type":"paragraph","text":"五日电悉。","index":2,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"33653cb56f","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）你们万余人进驻运城地区，必须向所有人员讲明对待当地人民及党政军的正确态度。","index":3,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"b205538121","type":"paragraph","text":"（二）中央已决定将北起赵城、南至蒲州沿同蒲线及其以西地区划归你们管辖，你们应准备有关接收及管理事宜，不要因接收引起人员的不满及物资的损失。具体的移交、接收及划界，望华北局拟出办法通知晋绥分局及当地党政军机关，务使划分以后不至引起不满及损失。","index":4,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"1c569c27bd","type":"paragraph","text":"（三）至少在一个时期内，分局应将自己的注意力主要地放在接收各县的工作上。","index":5,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"f6585c671e","type":"paragraph","text":"（四）分局应将工业生产问题放在领导工作的重要位置。有了工业生产的条件，党如果不注意恢复及发展工业，党的领导人员如果缺乏工业方面的知识，如果不用力去学会这一方面的知识，那就会要犯错误。在收复延安后，西北局亦须注意恢复及发展工业。","index":6,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"530f4b9213","type":"paragraph","text":"中央","index":7,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}},{"id":"6c06faf95e","type":"paragraph","text":"十一日","index":8,"publicationId":"wenji5","articleId":"079314b3f6","publication":{},"article":{}}],"page":{"start":109,"end":108}}}},"__N_SSG":true}